              <li class="mb-1 concerns-li"><span class="text-primary h5 me-2 concerns-span"><i class="uil uil-smile-beam align-middle"></i></span>A IA pode criar rapidamente modelos de dados, paginas e workflows</li>
              <li class="mb-1 concerns-li"><span class="text-primary h5 me-2 concerns-span"><i class="uil uil-smile-beam align-middle"></i></span>As pessoas podem refinar rapidamente a interface e as interacoes</li>
